Can we control it?

976
01:03:39,180 --> 01:03:40,180
飞回家
Fly us home?

977
01:03:44,170 --> 01:03:45,090
-斯塔克  -嗯
- Stark? - Yeah.

978
01:03:45,090 --> 01:03:46,420
