我听到了
Yeah, I heard you.

980
01:03:49,360 --> 01:03:51,190
我在想  或许我们不该回去
I'm thinking I'm not so sure we should.

981
01:03:52,410 --> 01:03:53,780
我们决不能
Under no circumstances

982
01:03:53,780 --> 01:03:56,330
把时间宝石送去灭霸那里
can we bring the Time Stone to Thanos.

983
01:03:56,720 --> 01:03:58,030
你恐怕还不明白
I don't think you quite understand

984
01:03:58,030 --> 01:03:59,310
-事情的严重性吧  -什么  不
