I saved you.

1019
01:06:30,360 --> 01:06:31,060
不
No.

1020
01:06:32,960 --> 01:06:36,310
不  我们在母星上时  本来很幸福
No. We were happy on my home planet.

1021
01:06:36,310 --> 01:06:37,890
