You're insane.

1032
01:07:03,560 --> 01:07:05,760
小家伙  这只是简单的数学
Little one, it's a simple calculus.

1033
01:07:05,760 --> 01:07:09,050
宇宙是有限的  资源也是有限的
This universe is finite, its resources finite.

1034
01:07:09,050 --> 01:07:13,120
如果生命不加以控制  就会消亡
If life is left unchecked, life will cease to exist.

1035
