1149
01:14:32,160 --> 01:14:33,640
中子星熄灭了
The star's gone out.

1150
01:14:34,840 --> 01:14:36,340
环也冻住了
And the rings are frozen.

1151
01:14:57,250 --> 01:14:58,260
希望这些矮人
I hope these dwarves

1152
01:14:58,260 --> 01:15:00,610
铸造的本事比打扫强
are better at forging than they are cleaning.

1153
01:15:05,760 --> 01:15:06,650
或许他们是意识到
Maybe they realized that

1154
01:15:06,650 --> 01:15:09,070
自己住在太空里的一个垃圾堆里
they live in a junk pile in the middle of space.

1155
01:15:09,080 --> 01:15:11,810
这个锻炉几世纪都没熄过火了
This forge hasn't gone dark in centuries.

1156
01:15:14,320 --> 01:15:17,180
你说灭霸有个手套  是吧
You said Thanos had a gauntlet, right?

1157
01:15:17,180 --> 01:15:18,450
对  怎么
Yes, why?

1158
01:15:18,600 --> 01:15:20,280
像那样的吗
It look anything like that?

1159
01:15:23,850 --> 01:15:25,590
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1160
01:15:25,800 --> 01:15:26,960
回飞行舱去
Go back to the pod.

1161
01:15:31,650 --> 01:15:32,820
伊特里  等等
Eitri, wait!

1162
01:15:33,440 --> 01:15:34,180
住手
Stop!

1163
01:15:35,480 --> 01:15:36,180
住手
Stop.

1164
01:15:37,240 --> 01:15:38,170
托尔
Thor?

1165
01:15:41,350 --> 01:15:42,670
这里发生了什么
What happened here?

1166
01:15:43,130 --> 01:15:45,650
你本该保护我们的
You were supposed to protect us.

1167
01:15:46,350 --> 01:15:49,160
阿斯加德本该保护我们的
Asgard was supposed to protect us.

1168
01:15:49,210 --> 01:15:51,550
阿斯加德被毁了
Asgard is destroyed.

1169
01:15:53,670 --> 01:15:57,150
伊特里  手套  你做了什么
Eitri, the glove. What did you do?

1170
01:16:10,140 --> 01:16:13,000
环上住了300个矮人
300 dwarves lived on this ring.

1171
01:16:14,640 --> 01:16:17,610
我以为如果我听从他的命令  他们就会安全
I thought if I did what he asked, they'd be safe.

1172
01:16:20,020 --> 01:16:21,700
我造出了他要的东西
I made what he wanted.

1173
01:16:23,250 --> 01:16:27,570
一件能汲取宝石力量的装置
A device capable of harnessing the power of the stones.

1174
01:16:29,720 --> 01:16:34,130
然后他还是杀了所有人
Then he killed everyone anyway.

1175
01:16:36,790 --> 01:16:38,300
除了我
All except me.

1176
01:16:39,640 --> 01:16:41,740
"你的命属于你"  他说
"Your life is yours," He said.

1177
01:16:42,710 --> 01:16:46,850
"但你的手  属于我"
"But your hands are mine alone."

1178
01:16:47,530 --> 01:16:49,840
伊特里  你的手不是重点
Eitri, this isn't about your hands.

1179
01:16:50,800 --> 01:16:52,480
你设计的每一件武器
Every weapon you've ever designed,

1180
01:16:52,480 --> 01:16:54,040
每把斧子  锤子  剑
every axe, hammer, sword...

1181
01:16:54,050 --> 01:16:56,210
都在你脑袋里
it's all inside your head.

1182
01:16:57,170 --> 01:16:59,140
我知道你现在觉得希望尽失
Now, I know it feels like all hope is lost.

1183
01:16:59,140 --> 01:17:00,310
相信我  我知道
Trust me, I know.

1184
01:17:01,120 --> 01:17:05,900
但你我联手  我们能杀了灭霸
But together, you and I, we can kill Thanos.

1185
01:17:46,350 --> 01:17:48,680
螳螂  听好了
Mantis, listen very carefully.

1186
01:17:49,020 --> 01:17:50,890
我需要你去泰坦星见我
I need you to meet me on Titan.

1187
01:17:57,910 --> 01:17:58,560
怎么了
Hey, what's going on?

1188
01:17:58,570 --> 01:18:00,460
我们好像到了
I think we're here.

1189
01:18:00,460 --> 01:18:02,730
这玩意恐怕没有自动停车功能
I don't think this rig has a self-park function.

1190
01:18:04,400 --> 01:18:06,360
把手伸到方向装置里
Get your hand inside the steering gimbal.

1191
01:18:06,360 --> 01:18:07,530
把这个合上
Close those around it.

1192
01:18:08,700 --> 01:18:09,650
-懂吗  -好的
- You understand? - Yep, got it.

1193
01:18:09,650 --> 01:18:11,030
这是给一个大块头准备的
This was meant for one big guy,

1194
01:18:11,030 --> 01:18:13,510
-我们动作得同步  -好的  好了
- so we gotta move at the same time. - Okay, okay. Ready.

1195
01:18:17,740 --> 01:18:18,920
我们最好转向
We might wanna turn.

1196
01:18:18,930 --> 01:18:20,590
转向  转向啊
Turn! Turn! Turn!

1197
01:18:50,030 --> 01:18:50,720
你没事吧
You all right?

1198
01:18:53,170 --> 01:18:54,180
好悬啊
That was close.

1199
01:18:55,880 --> 01:18:56,670
我欠你的
I owe you one.

1200
01:18:57,560 --> 01:18:59,330
我想说  如果外星人
Let me just say, if aliens

1201
01:18:59,540 --> 01:19:01,710
在我胸腔里植入了卵什么的
wind up implanting eggs in my chest or something...

1202
01:19:01,710 --> 01:19:02,730
而我吃掉了你们谁  那我很抱歉
and I eat one of you, I'm sorry.

1203
01:19:02,730 --> 01:19:05,390
余下的时间里不许你
I do not want another single pop culture reference

1204
01:19:05,390 --> 01:19:06,750
再提流行文化梗了  懂吗
out of you for the rest of the trip. You understand?

1205
01:19:06,750 --> 01:19:08,630
我是想说  有东西过来了
I'm trying to say that something is coming.

1206
01:19:15,710 --> 01:19:17,300
灭霸
Thanos!

1207
01:19:38,220 --> 01:19:39,700
拜托别把你的卵放进我身体里
Please don't put your eggs in me!

1208
01:19:41,770 --> 01:19:43,100
别动  小丑
Stay down, clown.

1209
01:19:48,920 --> 01:19:51,410
死吧  死亡毯子
Die, blanket of death!

1210
01:19:56,980 --> 01:20:00,230
都别动  都给我冷静
Everybody stay where you are. Chill the eff out.

1211
01:20:01,090 --> 01:20:02,910
我就问你一次
I'm gonna ask you this one time.

1212
01:20:03,840 --> 01:20:04,960
卡魔拉呢
Where is Gamora?

1213
01:20:04,960 --> 01:20:07,780
我问你个更好的  卡魔拉是谁
Yeah. I'll do you one better. Who's Gamora?

1214
01:20:08,090 --> 01:20:10,850
我问你个更好的  为什么卡魔拉
I'll do you one better. Why is Gamora?

1215
01:20:10,850 --> 01:20:12,780
告诉我她在哪  否则我发誓
Tell me where the girl is or I swear to you

1216
01:20:12,780 --> 01:20:14,130
我会把这小怪物烧焦的
I'm gonna French fry this little freak.

1217
01:20:14,130 --> 01:20:17,270
来吧  你打我的人  我打你的人  来吧
Let's do it. You shoot my guy and I'll blast him. Let's go!

1218
01:20:17,850 --> 01:20:20,450
动手吧  奎尔  我承受得住
Do it, Quill! I can take it.

1219
01:20:20,450 --> 01:20:21,520
不  他承受不住
No, he can't take it!

1220
01:20:21,520 --> 01:20:22,450
她说得对  你承受不住
She's right. You can't.

1221
01:20:22,450 --> 01:20:24,810
是吗  你不告诉我她在哪吗  好啊
Oh, yeah? You don't wanna tell me where she is? That's fine.

1222
01:20:24,810 --> 01:20:26,000
我杀了你们三个
I'll kill all three of you

1223
01:20:26,000 --> 01:20:28,170
然后揍到灭霸开口
and I'll beat it out of Thanos myself.

1224
01:20:28,170 --> 01:20:29,080
从你开始
Starting with you.

1225
01:20:29,080 --> 01:20:30,190
等等  灭霸
Wait, what, Thanos?

1226
01:20:30,190 --> 01:20:32,530
好吧  我问你个问题
All right, let me ask you this one time.

1227
01:20:32,970 --> 01:20:34,860
你效忠哪位主人
What master do you serve?

1228
01:20:34,860 --> 01:20:35,930
我效忠哪位主人
What master do I serve?

1229
01:20:35,930 --> 01:20:37,860
怎么  我该说"耶稣"吗
What am I supposed to say, "Jesus"?

1230
01:20:38,900 --> 01:20:39,630
你是地球人
You're from Earth.

1231
01:20:39,630 --> 01:20:40,570
我不是地球人  我是密苏里人
I'm not from Earth, I'm from Missouri.

1232
01:20:40,570 --> 01:20:42,080
那就是地球  白痴
Yeah, that's on Earth, dipshit.

1233
01:20:42,080 --> 01:20:43,030
你打我们干什么
What are you hassling us for?

1234
01:20:43,040 --> 01:20:44,940
你们不是灭霸的人
So you're not with Thanos?

1235
01:20:45,670 --> 01:20:47,460
灭霸的人
With Thanos?

1236
01:20:48,180 --> 01:20:50,660
不  我是来杀灭霸的
No, I'm here to kill Thanos.

1237
01:20:50,820 --> 01:20:52,730
他带走了我女人  等等  你们是谁
He took my girl. Wait, who are you?

1238
01:20:53,570 --> 01:20:55,050
我们是复仇者  哥们
We're the Avengers, man.

1239
01:20:55,050 --> 01:20:57,650
你们是托尔说的人
You're the ones Thor told us about.

1240
01:20:57,790 --> 01:20:58,850
你们认识托尔
You know Thor?

1241
01:20:59,100 --> 01:20:59,800
是啊
Yeah.

1242
01:21:00,040 --> 01:21:03,020
高个  长得不咋样  还需要别人救
Tall guy, not that good-looking, needed saving.

1243
01:21:03,020 --> 01:21:04,060
他现在在哪
Where is he now?

1244
01:21:19,590 --> 01:21:21,480
这就是你的计划  用砖头拍他
This is the plan? We're gonna hit him with a brick?

1245
01:21:21,480 --> 01:21:22,760
这是模具
It's a mold.

1246
01:21:23,860 --> 01:21:25,060
国王的武器
A king's weapon.

1247
01:21:25,610 --> 01:21:27,770
本该是阿斯加德最强大的
Meant to be the greatest in Asgard.

1248
01:21:28,610 --> 01:21:31,550
理论上  它甚至能召唤彩虹桥
In theory, it could even summon the Bifrost.

1249
01:21:31,670 --> 01:21:32,740
它有名字吗
Did it have a name?

1250
01:21:34,370 --> 01:21:35,560
风暴斧
Stormbreaker.

1251
01:21:36,040 --> 01:21:37,250
有点过了
That's a bit much.

1252
01:21:39,120 --> 01:21:40,330
要怎么打造它
So how do we make it?

1253
01:21:42,080 --> 01:21:44,010
你得重启锻炉
You'll have to restart the forge.

1254
01:21:45,290 --> 01:21:47,510
唤醒濒死恒星的核心
Awaken the heart of a dying star.

1255
01:21:50,050 --> 01:21:52,580
兔子  启动飞行舱
Rabbit, fire up the pod.

1256
01:21:56,340 --> 01:21:58,190
这星球遭遇了什么
The hell happened to this planet?

1257
01:21:58,450 --> 01:22:00,210
偏离自转轴八度
It's eight degrees off its axis.

1258
01:22:00,210 --> 01:22:02,750
引力到处都是
Gravitational pull is all over the place.

1259
01:22:03,830 --> 01:22:06,620
我们有一个优势  他会自己来
Yeah, we got one advantage. He's coming to us.

1260
01:22:07,710 --> 01:22:08,640
我们要利用这一点
We'll use it.

1261
01:22:09,090 --> 01:22:10,450
好了  我有个计划
All right, I have a plan.

1262
01:22:10,540 --> 01:22:11,840
至少有个大致轮廓
Or at least the beginnings of one.

1263
01:22:11,840 --> 01:22:13,150
非常简单  我们引他过来
It's pretty simple. We draw him in,

1264
01:22:13,150 --> 01:22:14,590
把他打趴下  拿到需要的东西
pin him down, get what we need.

1265
01:22:14,710 --> 01:22:16,000
我可不想跟他纠缠[陪他跳舞]
Definitely don't wanna dance with this guy.

1266
01:22:16,000 --> 01:22:17,700
我们只想拿手套
We just want the gauntlet.

1267
01:22:18,070 --> 01:22:19,350
你打哈欠
Are you yawning?

1268
01:22:20,540 --> 01:22:22,440
我讲解计划的时候你竟然打哈欠
In the middle of this, while I'm breaking it down?

1269
01:22:22,710 --> 01:22:24,070
你听见我说的了吗
Did you hear what I said?

1270
01:22:24,550 --> 01:22:26,910
你说"我们需要计划"之后我就没在听了
I stopped listening after you said, "We need a plan."

1271
01:22:26,910 --> 01:22:28,420
好吧  他沉浸在自己的世界里
Okay, Mr. Clean is on his own page.

1272
01:22:28,420 --> 01:22:30,880
他们一般不会"不随机应变"
See, "Not winging it" isn't really what they do.

1273
01:22:30,880 --> 01:22:32,970
那他们都会什么
Uh, what exactly is it that they do?

1274
01:22:32,970 --> 01:22:34,660
打仇恨  拉群架
Kick names, take ass.

1275
01:22:34,660 --> 01:22:35,760
没错
Yeah, that's right.

1276
01:22:42,740 --> 01:22:44,280
好了  请各位都过来
All right, just get over here, please.

1277
01:22:44,490 --> 01:22:46,470
爵先生  能不能让你的伙伴们围过来
Mr. Lord, can you get your folks to circle up?

1278
01:22:46,470 --> 01:22:48,560
别爵先生  叫我星爵就好
"Mr. Lord." Star-Lord is fine.

1279
01:22:51,460 --> 01:22:52,650
我们得联合起来
We gotta coalesce.

1280
01:22:52,650 --> 01:22:54,610
因为如果我们只凭一腔勇气去面对他
'Cause if all we come at him with is a plucky attitude...

1281
01:22:54,610 --> 01:22:57,120
哥们  别说什么一腔勇气
Dude, don't call us plucky.

1282
01:22:57,210 --> 01:22:58,610
我们不知道那是什么意思
We don't know what it means.

1283
01:22:58,720 --> 01:23:01,360
我们很乐观  我喜欢你的计划
All right, we're optimistic, yes. I like your plan.

1284
01:23:01,360 --> 01:23:04,020
只不过它烂透了  让我来做计划
Except it sucks, so let me do the plan...

1285
01:23:04,030 --> 01:23:06,030
这样就完美无缺了
and that way it might be really good.

1286
01:23:06,030 --> 01:23:08,170
告诉他你斗舞拯救宇宙的事
Tell him about the dance-off to save the universe.

1287
01:23:08,170 --> 01:23:10,290
-什么斗舞  -不值一提
- What dance-off? - It's nothing.

1288
01:23:10,290 --> 01:23:11,550
就像那部电影《浑身是劲》一样
Like in Footloose, the movie?

1289
01:23:11,550 --> 01:23:12,980
就是《浑身是劲》那样
Exactly like Footloose.

1290
01:23:13,720 --> 01:23:15,420
它依然是史上最棒的电影吗
Is it still the greatest movie in history?

1291
01:23:15,420 --> 01:23:16,480
从来都不是
It never was.

1292
01:23:16,660 --> 01:23:17,750
别打岔  好不好
Don't encourage this, all right?

1293
01:23:17,750 --> 01:23:18,900
-好  -这位飞侠哥顿
- Okay. - We're getting no help

1294
01:23:18,900 --> 01:23:20,600
-帮不上我们什么  -《飞侠哥顿》
- from Flash Gordon here. - Flash Gordon?

1295
01:23:20,600 --> 01:23:22,580
那可是在夸我哦
By the way, that's a compliment.

1296
01:23:22,600 --> 01:23:24,160
别忘了  我有一半人类血统
Don't forget, I'm half human.

1297
01:23:24,160 --> 01:23:26,110
也就是说我有一半的蠢
So that 50% of me that's stupid...

1298
01:23:26,950 --> 01:23:28,120
而你是百分百的蠢
that's 100% you.

1299
01:23:28,120 --> 01:23:29,640
我真佩服你数学这么好
Your math is blowing my mind.

1300
01:23:29,640 --> 01:23:30,680
打扰一下
Excuse me.

1301
01:23:31,740 --> 01:23:35,310
你的朋友经常那样吗
But does your friend often do that?

1302
01:23:36,570 --> 01:23:38,660
斯特兰奇  没事吧
Strange, we all right?

1303
01:23:49,210 --> 01:23:50,250
你恢复了  你没事
You're back. You're all right.

1304
01:23:51,330 --> 01:23:52,390
你刚刚怎么了
Hey, what was that?

1305
01:23:52,570 --> 01:23:56,620
我推进了时间  浏览未来的可能性
I went forward in time to view alternate futures.

1306
01:23:57,170 --> 01:23:59,960
看即将到来的一战所有可能出现的结果
To see all the possible outcomes of the coming conflict.

1307
01:24:01,390 --> 01:24:02,610
你看到了多少种
How many did you see?

1308
01:24:02,920 --> 01:24:05,370
一千四百万六百零五种
14,000,605.

1309
01:24:06,810 --> 01:24:07,850
我们赢了几种
How many did we win?

1310
01:24:13,020 --> 01:24:13,730
一种
One.

1311
01:24:36,110 --> 01:24:38,120
灵魂宝石最好在山上
The stone had better be up there.

1312
01:24:40,980 --> 01:24:42,550
不然你妹妹就完了
For your sister's sake.

1313
01:25:03,590 --> 01:25:08,590
欢迎  灭霸  阿拉尔斯之子
Welcome, Thanos, son of Alars.

1314
01:25:10,720 --> 01:25:14,050
卡魔拉  灭霸之女
Gamora, daughter of Thanos.

1315
01:25:14,180 --> 01:25:15,210
你认识我们
You know us?

1316
01:25:15,310 --> 01:25:19,560
我被诅咒认识所有来到此地的人
It is my curse to know all who journey here.

1317
01:25:20,500 --> 01:25:22,170
灵魂宝石在哪
Where is the Soul Stone?

1318
01:25:22,900 --> 01:25:24,090
你应该知道
You should know...

1319
01:25:25,220 --> 01:25:27,980
得到它的代价极大
it extracts a terrible price.

1320
01:25:29,730 --> 01:25:31,050
我准备好了
I am prepared.

1321
01:25:33,670 --> 01:25:35,890
我们一开始都这么以为
We all think that at first.

1322
01:25:40,720 --> 01:25:42,550
但我们都错了
We are all wrong.

1323
01:25:54,570 --> 01:25:56,660
你怎么如此熟悉这里
How is it you know this place so well?

1324
01:25:57,020 --> 01:26:01,260
上一世我也想找无限宝石
A lifetime ago, I, too, sought the stones.

1325
01:26:01,760 --> 01:26:04,220
甚至曾把一个攥在手里过
I even held one in my hand.

1326
01:26:04,690 --> 01:26:08,490
但它把我流放到这里
But it cast me out, banished me here.

1327
01:26:09,110 --> 01:26:12,960
指引别人寻找我无法拥有的珍宝
Guiding others to a treasure I cannot possess.

1328
01:26:21,640 --> 01:26:24,670
你所寻找的就在你面前
What you seek lies in front of you.

1329
01:26:25,500 --> 01:26:27,190
你所害怕的也在那里
As does what you fear.

1330
01:26:28,590 --> 01:26:29,520
